channel.title: Is the Moparscape Server status list not working or something?
channel.description: Not meaning to post in the wrong topic but I didn't know which one to post it in. But I put my server on Moparscape server status waited the 30 minutes and such. Whats going on? :S I also noticed only like 6-7 servers are on there which is hard to believe considering this place is always 3-4 pages + filled with servers.

item.title: Is the Moparscape Server status list not working or something?
item.dc:creator: @NewbieNewty Newty
item.description:
@NewbieNewty wrote:

Thecheeseman11:

Newty I noticed half your posts are “use the search button”. Well how about this, NO. because I usually never find what im looking for when an asshole takes the time to go through and read each post and post"use the search button". Thanks Koopa… was just wondering because my first day back into hosting a server in a couple months.

No, I post that answer when I know the answer is easily obtainable.

Need proof, check the announcement section: http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,363840.0.html
